collectible.name: CryptoStellas 2022 Rugburn New Year’s Party: Chalice Dark
collectible.description:
Everyone who attends the Rugburn New Year’s Party at Stellabelle’s Cryptovoxels gallery will receive a chalice for free, either light or dark version: https://www.cryptovoxels.com/play?coords=S@724W,671S
Party starts at 1 PM CST on January 1, 2022. Activities include: burning of rugpull NFTs, dancing together in the fire, cleansing rituals, champagne, DJ, auction of 3 CryptoStellas: Satan, Azealia Banks, and Pranksy: https://opensea.io/collection/cryptostellas
Happy New Year!
collectible.author: 0xf1182c5e5bcd7c90b04eb14eb4f971c52f510d47

collectible.name: CryptoStella Rug for 2022 New year
collectible.description: Rugburn Party on New Year’s Day: Start the new year out right by throwing rugpull NFTs into the fire! Yes, there will be fire. Yes, everyone who attends gets a free rug wearable.Yes, there will be free drinks! Yes, we will be dancing around the fire, and on the rooftop dance floor, DJ is Angie. And yes, we will be walking through rituals to cleanse ourselves of the dirty rugs! See you there!
